# Billiard Domain Rules

- Use standard Glicko-2 outcome scoring: win/loss only (no score-margin weighting like 10:1 vs 10:9).
- Team matches (`2v2`, `3v3`) must always be unrated and never modify Glicko-2 values.
- Tournament participants must have registered accounts; no guest/anonymous tournament players.
- Rated results must update both players in 1v1 matches, including provisional players.
- UI must clearly label team matches as `Unrated Team Match`.
